            , (Police-constable B 60.) I found this bag and 4s. 6d. in it on the prisoner.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was at the Durham Arms, and saw this bag under the table - I took it up, not knowing whose it was; it had 2l. 4s. and some copper in it.</p>
